caption.title: Posterior R 0 estimates for Texas counties for each month using historic temperature data for running estimation procedure and priors.
caption.p: Fill color indicates the estimated Median or 99 percentile estimate for that county for the given month, with counties showing yellow or red indicating their R 0 is above one (labels). Estimates are made using all importations through December of 2016, and assuming a single transmission event in November.
